ForwardArrow2ShapeRealizer

public ForwardArrow2ShapeRealizer(double arrowLength,
                                  double heightDecrease)
Constructs a ForwardArrow2ShapeRealizer to draw alternate arrow shapes with the passed arrow length and height decrease.

Parameters:
arrowLength - The length of the arrow part to use.
heightDecrease - A proportion of thickness of the straight part and arrow head part of the arrow (1.0 is no decrease). So controls difference between this (--->) and this(==>)
